<section class="section2" id="AboutUs">
  <table>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <img
          class="wow animate__animated animate__slideInRight"
          style="height: 250px"
          src="/Images/Technology Integration.jpeg"
          alt="AboutUs"
        />
      </td>
      <td>
        <span class="title" style="font-size: 23px"
          >Technology Integration</span
        >
        <p class="ph wow animate__animated animate__slideInRight">
          Digital transformation involves the adoption and integration of
          various digital technologies across the organization. This includes
          technologies such as cloud computing, big data analytics, artificial
          intelligence (AI), machine learning, Internet of Things (IoT),
          blockchain, and automation.By leveraging these technologies,
          organizations can streamline operations, optimize processes, and
          unlock new opportunities.
        </p>
        <p class="wow animate__animated animate__slideInRight">
